high_descs: Go to the counter behind you, near the coffee maker.
Take the mug from the coffee maker.
Turn right and go to the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge.
Return to the coffee maker to the left.
Place the mug at the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug at the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the coffee pot.
Pick up the white cup that is on the coffee machine.
Turn right and move to the refrigerator. Open the fridge.
Place the white cup on the shelf in the fridge. Close the door and allow cup to cool.
Open fridge.  Pick up the white cup that is on the shelf.  Close the fridge.
Turn left and go back to the coffee pot.  Put the cup on the coffee pot.
Pick up the mug from the coffee machine.
Bring the mug to the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge.
Bring the mug to the coffee machine.
Put the mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on the coffee machine.
